page.title: 16Clubs for kids in Bromsgrove
page.content: This a survey on some of the clubs people go to in and around Bromsgrove. 20.6% go to Guides.13.7% go to Dancing .27.5% go to the B.Y.O. 10.3% go to Netball.13.7% go to Gym.6.8% go to Girls Brigade.6.8% go to Horse Riding. 3.4% go to the Youth Club.3.4% are Aston Villa supporters.6.8% belong to the Puffin Club.13.7% go to Cubs. 3.4% go to the Rugby Club.10.3% go to Scouts.10.3% go to Swimming Club.3.4% go to Tennis.3.4% go to Squash.6.8% belong to St.John's Ambulance.3.4% go to Boy's Club.3.4% play for Cloverdale Rangers Football Club.6.8% go to Brownies. {Scouts:}Once you leave Cubs you can join Scouts.There you do a Membership badge which involves doing an outdoor actvity,talking with your patrol leader.At Scouts we go canoing,carving tent pegs,camping hikes and making
